<h1>Software Design Approaches</h1>


<font color=red>
<h2>TOP DOWN</h2>

Problem well understood<br>
Apply divide-and-conquer approach<br>
</font>
Data processing applications, scientific applications,
and utility programs (compilers, editors, etc.)<br>

Design techniques include:
<ul>
stepwise refinement<br>
integrated top-down development<br>
structured design<br>
Jackson structured programming
</ul>

